; Coverage test for post.cc
; Tests get_code (returns xact code) and get_has_cost for postings.
; The code field comes from the parent transaction.
; has_cost indicates whether a posting has a cost annotation.

2024/03/01 (REF123) Purchase
    Expenses:Food     100 EUR @ $1.10
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(code) %(has_cost)\n"
REF123 true
REF123 false
end test
